tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I had an exceptional experience at Dental Planet. Dr. Rajesh k Reddy  provided top-notch care for my chronic dental issue. His professionalism and expertise were evident throughout the treatment. The facility is well-maintained, and the staff ensures a clean environment. Communication was excellent; they explained my condition thoroughly and addressed all my concerns. The quality of care surpassed my expectations. I highly recommend Dental Planet, especially for the outstanding service provided by Dr. Rajesh.

Examined and explained the problems of various teeth. Suggested the course of action and time schedule. Neither i had asked nor he mentioned the cost of proposed treatment.Afterwords, the first job ' cleaning of teeth' is completed by one of his Assistant Doctors.Next appointment fixed for 15.11.2016 at 5.00 pm. Explained the problems and solutions/ tips for better management of teeth clearly.
as per my office, the estimate of treatment is required and the same may be sent on my mail ID. krrao50@gmail.com. pl ensure forwarding the estimate for taking approval from my organisation

Thanks

Receives patient with a pleasant smile which makes patient half relieved from the problem. (Counselling) explaining about the problem and the treatment to be given with easily understandable examples was excellent. Undergone Root Canal Treatment and also Tooth Extraction but there was no pain at all during the treatment.  I mean the treatment was done with such perfection that the patient feels fully comfortable. The follow up Appointments are given as per (Our) Patients convenient days and times.

review: He is very professional.  He took mmediate recovery action for my wound in my tounge by referring and taking me to another specialist. He took my fear off and wound off while the first gwnneral physcian whom  I met scared me stating it is cancer stage 1.

Dr Rajesh ensures to familiarize with detailed explanation and provides complete guidance thus helps us feel comfortable and confident and we can choose the best options. We were quite thankful to Dr Rajesh *** *** **** ********* *** ********** **** *******

Dr. Rajesh K Reddy was very good and quick in extracting the tooth and he suggested some medicine after that.We were happy that everything will be perfect after that.But it started swelling in no time including pain.We called doctor for a solution but someone else picked up the phone, so we had to rush again within 2 days of extraction. Got it checked by another doctor and she changed the old medicines and suggested another set of medicines.Not sure how soon this can be sorted.

context: Teeth Sensitive to Hot and Cold,Toothache,
review: Experience has been really bad. It has been a year since I took my mother for tooth removal n she still has acute pain when she eats or talks and it is so annoying to see her suffer daily. Didn't know that a simple procedure of tooth removal could cause so much trouble. Dr Rajesh gives very knowledgeable talk, wish he could've applied some of it during tooth extraction. I only wish he takes more care while attending to elder patients.

It was very gud especially the way doctor rajesh explained the problem its causes and alternative solutions depending upon our comfort. Most importantly want to add that this clinic and this particular doctor rajesh is unlike other commercial dentists and clinics. Here we can be assured of not being treated commercially but truly for our pain with affection and very cost effective. I strongly recommend Dr. Rajesh bcoz of his knowlede and patience in treating his patients.

Dr.rajesh is an exceptionally good doctor...very friendly...with a positive attitude..he explains everything in detail and has given good advice...really happy after the treatment .......... going to recommended Dr.rajesh to my friends and family .......:) :):)

it was very detailed and in simple terms at the same time. Things went very fast and accurate. Not only my current problem was addressed but also other things which I considered as minor and need no attention were also mentioned and were given appropriately
